            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間26日01:32，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/HSI\">恆生指數</a>下跌505.53點（或2%），暫報24830.42點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-2.65%</li><li>近 1 月：-5.34%</li><li>近 3 月：-1.87%</li><li>近 6 月：-4.34%</li><li>今年以來：-1.15%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>禽畜肉類概念領跌-6.52%。其中    惠生國際(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01340:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01340\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01340-HK</a>)            下跌        16.33%            ;        雨潤食品(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01068:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01068\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01068-HK</a>)            下跌        8.62%            ;        中糧家佳康(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01610:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01610\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01610-HK</a>)            下跌        5%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>採購及供應鏈管理概念領跌-4.72%。其中    中遠海運國際(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00517:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00517\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00517-HK</a>)            下跌        6.28%            ;        卓爾智聯(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02098:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article